      "content": "exactly. that's the thing. it feels like i'm just a ghost in this house now. i look at his side of the bed and i just... i don't see a reason to wake up tomorrow. it feels like the version of me that was happy died with him. everything is just heavy and gray. i just want the weight to stop.",
