    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"letting go of the pain\"... what does that actually mean? i feel like i've tried everything to make it stop, but it just stays. i look at his pictures and i just feel like we were supposed to be together forever. it feels like the only way to actually find peace is to be where he is. i don't see how things ever get better than this.",
